Package: sfsutils
Title: Parsing of site-frequency spectra (SFS) from VCF files
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R:
    person("Janek", "Sendrowski", , "sendrowski.janek@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An R wrapper for the 'sfsutils' Python package which provides fast and flexible parsing of site-frequency spectra (SFS) from VCF files, including annotation, filtration, and stratification of sites.
